Minister of Environmental Affairs Edna Molewa has died, the SABC reported on Saturday. She was 61 years old. Before being appointed to her current post, she was the minister of Social Development and Premier of the North West. The presidency was expected to issue a statement on Saturday. More to follow. https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/breaking-minister-edna-molewa-has-died-reports-20180922